---
title: Pumpkin & Basil Pesto Risotto with Plant-Based Parmesan & Pine Nut Pangrattato
description: This rich, creamy risotto comes together in the oven, leaving you free to create a quick and crunchy pine nut pangrattato to sprinkle over at the end. Such a small factor takes this plant-based veggie meal to the next level – taste it and see!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pumpkin-basil-pesto-risotto-928eb21f.jpg
